Text: If you withdraw the money for a purpose other than qualified education costs, you may owe income tax and a 10-percent tax penalty on withdrawn earnings.
Cause: If you withdraw the money for a purpose other than qualified education costs
Effect: you may owe income tax and a 10-percent tax penalty on withdrawn earnings.
